{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And one of the guys who was an inmate also, who was operating the showers, saw me every morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was running to be one of the first ones to wash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he told me, he says, Ben, he says, you know, you come so early.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He says, you can come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, there were a lot of people which were taking showers in the morning, privileged ones, or there might be some SS, he says.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But we have some of the people which are operating the barracks which are all day in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They-- they come and take a shower too, he says.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And from then on, I could take a shower almost any time in the morning first.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So cleanliness was a part of your survival, cleanliness on top of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Also, of course, the longer you were in the camps, I mentioned a-- a-- it just came to my mind the-- the incident.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Yes, I was-- it was curfew time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And whether I was running, before my brother joined me or so, joined our-- our kommando, I was late.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Curfew, for example, is six o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And anyone seen after six o'clock, I mean, you got problems and trouble.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the-- lagerkommandant we called them-- he was also an inmate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he was also a German, and he was a-- he was a killer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And of course, he called me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He stopped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was walking, and he stopped me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he raised his hand to hit me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he noticed my number, which we have in here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And he looked at my number, and he says, you old-- called me bandit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He says, you should know better than running now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It's curfew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I just told him the truth.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
